'''西海水闸'''，又名：'''南浦水闸'''，是[[朝鲜民主主义人民共和国|朝鲜]][[大同江|大同江]]出海口上修建的一座{{en-link|防潮堤|tidal barrage}}，位于[[南浦特別市|南浦特別市]]以西15公里<ref name=dljs/>。水闸将大同江与黄海隔开，大堤长8公里，有三道船闸，可通过50,000吨级海轮。水闸建于1981年，举全国之力建设，至1986年竣工，约耗费40亿美元。此项水利工程的目标是为了阻挡黄海海水倒灌大同江<ref name=mafengwo>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/5504826.html |title=平安南道景点：西海水闸 |accessdate=2018-10-05 |work=mafengwo.cn |archive-date=2018-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181006035207/http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/5504826.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=dljs>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dljs.net/dlsk/9677.html |title=锁江镇海的南浦水闸 |accessdate=2018-10-05 |date=2010-01-29 |work=地理教师网 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181006083613/http://www.dljs.net/dlsk/9677.html |archive-date=2018-10-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>[https://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_detailpage&v=VHu5FEeIqfM#t=78 "West Sea Barrage"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_detailpage&v=VHu5FEeIqfM#t=78 |date=20170202025923 }}, ''TAEHA''. "The Taedong River, before the barrage was built, could not be used for agriculture and industry because it would become salty by the rising tide."</ref>，建立灌溉系统使得河口沿岸的土地适合耕种<ref name=dljs/><ref name=mafengwo/><ref>[http://www.fao.org/nr/water/aquastat/countries/korea_d_p_rp/print1.stm Democratic People´s Republic of Korea - Geography, climate and population] {{Wayback|url=http://www.fao.org/nr/water/aquastat/countries/korea_d_p_rp/print1.stm |date=20111029234722 }}, ''Food and Agriculture Organization of the United Nations'', 2010, Retrieved 2011-05-03</ref>。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://chinese.aljazeera.net/news/2018/6/7/russia-attempts-to-regain-clout-over-north-korea|title=俄罗斯有意重塑对朝鲜的影响|accessdate=2018-10-05|date=2018-06-07|work=aljazeera.net|archive-date=2019-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191130144048/https://chinese.aljazeera.net/news/2018/6/7/russia-attempts-to-regain-clout-over-north-korea|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=ifeng20170718/>

朝鲜官方将此工程视做本国建设的主要成就之一<ref>[http://www.travelthewholeworld.com/northkorea.html North Korea] {{Wayback|url=http://www.travelthewholeworld.com/northkorea.html |date=20110806161310 }}, ''Travel the Whole World'', Retrieved 2011-05-03</ref>，经常作为电视新闻播报的背景画面出现。它也是国际旅行团的行程安排中的常见景点。坝顶铺有公路连接两岸，与大坝相连小岛上建有游客中心，为游人播放介绍该工程的多国语影片。

